            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/464df75643b85d808ea7457d333c2520_6300775493071532339.png",
                "id": "talent70332",
                "key": "Cool-Color Capture",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cool-Color Capture"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>. Attach <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Snappy Silhouette</span> to the target.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Snappy Silhouette</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span> to the character(s) to which this is attached. If only 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> is remaining and the attached character is affected by <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>, this instance of DMG +1.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/54adbd6e0af44cff009737afb67b0409_7241470843411119598.png",
                "id": "talent85642",
                "key": "Framing: Freezing Point Composition",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Framing: Freezing Point Composition"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, heals all your characters for 1 HP, summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Newsflash Field</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/d1cf9afd3481f21b5ec894c5c65557fe_1038790914119607227.png",
                "id": "talent32706",
                "key": "Still Photo: Comprehensive Confirmation",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Still Photo: Comprehensive Confirmation"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, heal your active character for 1 HP.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8857093491677320583.png",
                "id": "talent17655",
                "key": "Newsflash Field",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/3ab60df4ef6812b4db37e62ef3338cfe_2978069340127782142.png",
                "title": "Newsflash Field"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Cryo and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_5788489425696131793.png",
